      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 20:21:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型科技公司与人工智能初创公司合作的一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/big-tech-s-year-of-partnering-up-with-ai-startups</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一批新的人工智能初创公司震撼了硅谷——以及更广阔的商业世界——今年全年，但有一件事没有改变：大型科技公司仍然掌握着权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/big-tech-s-year-of-partnering-up-with-ai-startups</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 19:49:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>有报道称亚马逊对地区体育网络感兴趣，辛克莱股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/sinclair-rises-on-report-amazon-interested-in-regional-networks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《华尔街日报》报道亚马逊公司正在洽谈投资该广播公司破产的钻石体育集团后，辛克莱公司股价上涨 7.6%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/sinclair-rises-on-report-amazon-interested-in-regional-networks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 19:26:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>专利丢失后苹果将停止在美国销售智能手表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/apple-to-stop-selling-some-apple-watch-models-on-patent-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于专利纠纷，苹果公司将停止在美国销售最新版本的智能手表，并在繁忙的假日季节将部分最畅销的设备撤出市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/apple-to-stop-selling-some-apple-watch-models-on-patent-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 15:27:52 GMT</pubDate>
